data.description: Are you looking for your next project? This charming fixer-upper located on historic Wilson Ave in beautiful Glendale, California, offers the perfect canvas for your creative vision. With 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a desirable location, this property presents an exciting opportunity for those with a flair for renovation and a desire to personalize their dream home. This home offers a spacious layout with three bedrooms, providing ample room for a growing family, a home office, or guest accommodations. The property is in need of some TLC, making it an ideal candidate for a renovation enthusiast. Customize the interior to your exact preferences and create a home that reflects your unique style. Wilson Ave is known for its tree-lined streets, and this property is situated in a sought-after Glendale neighborhood. Enjoy the convenience of being close to local schools, parks, shopping, dining, and easy access to major transportation routes. If you're ready to roll up your sleeves and turn this diamond in the rough into a gem, this fixer-upper in Glendale, CA is your chance to make it happen. Don't miss out on the potential this property holds. Huge lot with great possibility to build. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and explore the endless possibilities that await you on Wilson Ave.
